{"claim_id": "claim_006", "text": "The matrix directive produces a list of dictionaries (aka an array of objects) for the record.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "The \"matrix\" type produces a list \nof dictionaries (aka an array of objects) for the record.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_messes/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [4160, 4252], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.3390/metabo11030163", "spine_entity_ids": ["matrix_directive"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_024", "text": "The matrix directive creates a list of dictionaries by looping over all records in the indicated table.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "By default, this directive will loop over all records in the indicated table \nand build a dictionary for each record.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_messes/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [22795, 22912], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.3390/metabo11030163", "spine_entity_ids": ["matrix_directive"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_025", "text": "The collate field in matrix directives groups record data into dictionaries based on a specified field value.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "If given, the \nrecord data will be grouped into dictionaries based on their field value.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_messes/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [30226, 30314], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.3390/metabo11030163", "spine_entity_ids": ["collate_field"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_026", "text": "The fields_to_headers field changes matrix directive behavior to copy all fields from input records as is into the dictionary.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "The \"fields_to_headers\" field changes the behavior of the matrix directive so that \nby default all fields from input records are copied as is into the dictionary.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_messes/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [38164, 38326], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.3390/metabo11030163", "spine_entity_ids": ["matrix_directive", "fields_to_headers_field"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_027", "text": "The exclusion_headers field in matrix directives allows excluding specific fields from being added.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "The \n\"exclusion_headers\" field can then be used to exclude fields from being added.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_messes/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [38327, 38410], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.3390/metabo11030163", "spine_entity_ids": []}
{"claim_id": "claim_028", "text": "The values_to_str field in matrix directives can convert all field values to strings.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "The \"values_to_str\" field can also be used to convert all of the field values to strings.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_messes/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [5169, 5243], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.3390/metabo11030163", "spine_entity_ids": []}
